From the spacious eating nook featuring a 10 ft. ceiling, there is access to the deck overlooking the fully fenced backyard. An additional 2 bedrooms and 4 pc. bathroom with granite countertops completes the upper level. The family room in the fully developed walkout basement is a great secondary entertaining space. Additional features include air conditioning, a newer high efficiency furnace  &  hot water tank, and an attached double car garage. This home also features a new concrete front walkway, concrete side steps, and an oversized concrete pad wrap around the backyard offering a clean look to the property while also being functional. You'll always be just steps away from outdoor adventure thanks to the many community walking paths, parks, playgrounds, and green spaces that Tusc any has to offer!
